      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "9e9aed6e90633b02",
      "text": "This is a real problem today because those three levels of war are linked in complex ways, especially in the current global environment. The War Gaming Department (WGD) of the NWC is looking for ideas that will help improve the way it designs and produces wargames that cut across those levels of war more efficiently and effectively than heretofore. The NWC asked CNA to identify key game-design issues and to develop some recommendations for more effectively representing the linkage between the strategic, operational/strategic, and operational levels of war, especially as applied to future Navy Title X Global War Games (GWG)."
